    "3. **World Food Programme (WFP)**: Provides food assistance through food distribution and Cash and Voucher Assistance (CVA) programmes to improve food security.\n",
    "4. **Kenya Red Cross Society (KRCS)**: Delivers frontline humanitarian services, including emergency medical care, disaster response, water supply, family tracing, and support for new refugee arrivals at border entry points.\n",
